{"tid":1824992,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警搜查旺角上水單位拘4人　涉藏有及串謀製作爆炸品","createTime":"2020-01-15T02:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T02:52:02.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3e95f5c360dbeeaaee13b9bc55d71deabf68963d","tid":1824992,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:07:33.000Z","msg":"警方分別在旺角及上水兩個單位，拘捕4名21至29歲男子，他們涉嫌非法集結、藏有爆炸品、串謀製作爆炸品、藏毒及藏有工具可作非法用途。<br />\n<br />\n警員昨日在旺角通菜街截查3名目標男子，其後到通菜街一個單位搜查，發現一個長約8吋、重約1.5磅懷疑土製的金屬水喉管炸彈、頭盔、面具、懷疑防彈背心、一批易燃物及小量懷疑大麻。爆炸品處理課到場處理，並疏散附近居民，在受控情況下、於現場處理懷疑土製的金屬水喉管炸彈。警方經初步調查，相信這3名男子涉及今年1月1日旺角區的非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n警方亦在上水河霸村一間村屋，拘捕一名29歲本地男子，並於村屋內發現一批實驗室用品，如燒杯、量杯、化學物及電子設備。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502855-20200115.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502855-20200115.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=6674c554\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502855-20200115.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6d3d4c34\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502855-20200115.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4595d7f9c4528e67d0c70efbf041468ee7d400","tid":1824992,"uid":32899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e95f5c360dbeeaaee13b9bc55d71deabf68963d","tid":1824992,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:07:33.000Z","msg":"警方分別在旺角及上水兩個單位，拘捕4名21至29歲男子，他們涉嫌非法集結、藏有爆炸品、串謀製作爆炸品、藏毒及藏有工具可作非法用途。<br />\n<br />\n警員昨日在旺角通菜街截查3名目標男子，其後到通菜街一個單位搜查，發現一個長約8吋、重約1.5磅懷疑土製的金屬水喉管炸彈、頭盔、面具、懷疑防彈背心、一批易燃物及小量懷疑大麻。爆炸品處理課到場處理，並疏散附近居民，在受控情況下、於現場處理懷疑土製的金屬水喉管炸彈。警方經初步調查，相信這3名男子涉及今年1月1日旺角區的非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n警方亦在上水河霸村一間村屋，拘捕一名29歲本地男子，並於村屋內發現一批實驗室用品，如燒杯、量杯、化學物及電子設備。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502855-20200115.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502855-20200115.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerqcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=6674c554\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502855-20200115.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6d3d4c34\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502855-20200115.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:08:53.000Z","msg":"實驗室用品都拉"},{"pid":"2db89bbacc1237d170458587a4f335a3c1ad1b03","tid":1824992,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc9278919255b2014e786d66ae878a8cd9d8bc7","tid":1824992,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:18:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n自由市場開始收皮<br />\n為咗統一<br />\n大陸攬炒緊香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"5cd6f5cf289e99b6212d8f53938d3a5b2294d30b","tid":1824992,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:24:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n1.19 遮打道<br />\n1.22 荔枝角收押所</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HwugtoH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHwugtoH.jpg&h=a3dfe053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Eq7z3V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Eq7z3V.jpg&h=6484967a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XmELBM2.jpg\" data-